readable.content: A man is in the air with his bike and there 's another guy on his bike in the back with the water close by . Bicyclist ride the course near the ocean as the day comes to an end . Bikers getting airborne on a track near water and a skyline . The BMX bike rider jumps a grassy dirt ramp . Two BMX bikers jumping dirt ramps in front of a body of water .
